c: 4
v: 135
t: O ona verit ona bol absolutely equitable observe GOD when ona serve svedok vecer yourselves tvoj rodicia tvoj vztazny! Whether zalovat bol zirny chudobny GOD berie care z both Therefore nie biased tvoj personal zelat! Ona deviate disregard (this commandment) potom GOD je fully Cognizant z everything ona robit